WInJwhM9K","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recrHRx6nkLENhlpP","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recrHRx6nkLENhlpP","target":"recL1WV82pXaRBQ59","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recrHRx6nkLENhlpP","target":"recdMHFSmu222VnJG","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recrHRx6nkLENhlpP","target":"recR3zid90odgmB6g","label":"event"},{"source":"recrHRx6nkLENhlpP","target":"recN2veKNMtB7HzFi","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"reczJ9xCDoaD8Va2M","ref":"Matt.20.1","text":"For the kingdom of heaven is like unto a man that is an householder, which went out early in the morning to hire labourers into his vineyard.","year":33},{"id":"recnN0us4MPEHhFro","ref":"Matt.20.2","text":"And when he had agreed with the labourers for a penny a day, he sent them into his vineyard.","year":33},{"id":"recNOzgeUbm9AWYYC","ref":"Matt.20.3","text":"And he went out about the third hour, and saw others standing idle in the marketplace,","year":33},{"id":"rec2fXCgSPQTdpr3V","ref":"Matt.20.4","text":"And said unto them; Go ye also into the vineyard, and whatsoever is right I will give you. And they went their way.","year":33},{"id":"recpRVSlSKbVPdLl4","ref":"Matt.20.5","text":"Again he went out about the sixth and ninth hour, and did likewise.","year":33},{"id":"rec3PxRExFqPzQxpG","ref":"Matt.20.6","text":"And about the eleventh hour he went out, and found others standing idle, and saith unto them, Why stand ye here all the day idle?","year":33},{"id":"recjIXyYHg1CNEsrS","ref":"Matt.20.7","text":"They say unto him, Because no man hath hired us. He saith unto them, Go ye also into the vineyard; and whatsoever is right, that shall ye receive.","year":33},{"id":"rechGOA35aON2OlRm","ref":"Matt.20.8","text":"So when even was come, the lord of the vineyard saith unto his steward, Call the labourers, and give them their hire, beginning from the last unto the first.","year":33}]}
